**On Social Psychology**:
- Dunbar, R. - Research on social group size limits
- Haidt, J. - Work on moral foundations and social media effects
- Putnam, R. - Social capital research

**On Technology & Platforms**:
- Zuboff, S. - Surveillance capitalism analysis
- Wu, T. - Attention economics
- Winner, L. - Technology as politics

**On Institutional Dynamics**:
- Heterodox Academy - Viewpoint diversity research
- Edelman Trust Barometer - Annual trust surveys
- Scott, J.C. - Seeing Like a State (institutional legibility)

**On Economic/Family Structure**:
- Coontz, S. - Historical family research
- Case & Deaton - Deaths of despair research
- Murray, C. - Social capital decline

**On Measurement & Evaluation**:
- Ostrom, E. - Common pool resource management (institutional analysis)
- Senge, P. - Systems thinking approaches
- Meadows, D. - Leverage points in systems

